FBIS4-5572 "dreas070_d_94004" FBIS-EAS-94-070 Daily Report 12 Apr 1994 South Korea Meets With IAEA Head Hans Blix Meets With IAEA Head Hans Blix SK1204131694 Seoul KBS-1 Television Network in Korean 1231 GMT 12 Apr 94 SK1204131694 Seoul KBS-1 Television Network Korean BFN [Text] Foreign Minister Han Sung-chu met with Hans Blix, director-general of the International Atomic Energy Agency [IAEA], in Tokyo on 12 April. They shared the view that North Korea should allow an early additional inspection by the IAEA and again urged North Korea to allow inspections. Minister Han, who arrived in Tokyo today on his way to Russia, urged the above during a one-hour talk with IAEA Director-General Hans Blix, who was visiting Japan.
